description: [``botocore``] Add ComputationModelVersion support in IoT SiteWise APIs
[``botocore``] This release includes backward compatibility work on the "Expires" parameter.

[``botocore``] This release adds the RESOURCE_NOT_FOUND error code as a possible value in responses to the following operations: BatchGetStandardsControlAssociations, BatchUpdateStandardsControlAssociations, and BatchGetSecurityControls.
